description.title: Delivery
descriptions: Delivered directly to your home by trusted couriers like UPS, FedEx, or DHL, depending on your location
Delivery is free for orders above €100, with all costs, taxes, and customs fees covered by noo.ma
You can expect delivery in 2-4 business days within the EU and 3-8 business days for the UK, Switzerland, and Norway, starting from the dispatch date
All products from one order are being shipped together unless otherwise stated
